his Radio Canada video:%0a> %0a> https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VqBo7-dtLJA %0a> %0a> Justin Trudeau and many other Canadian citizens speak about the discomfort they feel as Francophones and Anglophones trying to fit into the Quebecois community. Many people in this video feel as if they are being marginalized or associated with incorrect groups due to their "incorrect" French usage. %0a> %0a> [[#contentends]]%0a> ----%0a> ----%0a> %0a> !!Expansions:%0a> [[#expansions]]%0a> %0a> [[#expansionsend]]%0a> %0a> ----%0a> %25red%25 '''Add an expansion:'''%0a> %0a> (:if [ exists GradebookExpansions.{$Name}-{$Author} || equal {$Author} {$:Author} ] :)%0a> %0a> (:else:)%0a> %0a> (:foxform Site.FoxForms#newexpansion:)%0a> %0a> (:ifend:)%0a> %0a> ----%0a> ----%0a> %0a> !!Comments%0a> %0a> %0a> %0a> (:section: :)%0a> (:Category: LinguisticDiscriminationInTheWild:)%0a\ No newline at end of file%0a
